@tag
Feature: login fuctionnality

  @tag1
  Scenario Outline: login is successful with valid credentials
    Given user in login  page
    When user enters <email>
    And click on next button
    And user enters <password>
    And clicks on validate button
    Then user is navigated to the home page

    Examples: 
      | email                   | password    |
      | dorsaf.othmen@talan.com | Dodo27948.! |

  @tag2
  Scenario Outline: login is successful with invalid credentials
    Given user in login  page
    When user enters invalid <email>
    And click on next button
    And user enters <password>
    And clicks on validate button
    Then user recived error message

    Examples: 
      | email                  | password    |
      | dorsaf.othmentalan.com | Dodo27948.! |

